                    <span>Anything I could say about this book would diminish its stellar qualities. You simply have to obtain a copy and read it! I have purchased more than a dozen copies, which have been given out as "here, read this" gifts. I suspect you'll find yourself doing the same :) Give a copy to all "thinking friends" and bright students you know.</span>
                  
              
